1.7.2.name: wordpress/dot-b
1.7.2.description: A simple, fresh and dot-decorated looking theme with a lot of basic theme-custom options  prepared for you to start you site. You can use those features : custom-background, custom-menu, drop-down menus, custom-header, widgets... and much more. Also you can recreate you child themes based on Dot-B. Compatible with WordPress 2.9+, valid XHTML & CSS + WP3 ready and Multi-language supported.
